                        <interp inst="t18750605-405-verdict-1" type="verdictSubcategory" value="no_subcategory"></interp>GUILTY</rs>
                  </hi>.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Various former convictions were, proved against the Prisoner.</hi>
